st and the chair of dreamworks animation skg inc she is a regular contributor on financial issues on cbs this morning and a spokesperson for the annual arielschwab black investor survey hobson serves on the board of many organizations including the chicago public education fund the lucas museum of narrative art and the sundance institute she is also a director of the starbucks corporation the estée lauder companies inc and dreamworks animation skg inc hobson has been acclaimed in selections such as times  time  list the magazines annual list of the one hundred most influential people in the world ebony magazines  leaders of the future  working women magazines  under   the world economic forums global leaders of tomorrow  esquires americas best and brightest  the wall street journals  women to watch  hobson created and hosted a show on abc on may   called unbroke what you need to know about money featuring celebrities such as the jonas brothers oscar the grouch and samuel l jackson actress vanessa l williams based her character selfmade businesswoman courtney paige in the american television drama the good wife on hobson studying her via hobsons ted talks in  hobson was named to head the economic club of chicago the first african american woman to do so personal lifeedit hobson began dating film director and producer george lucas in  after they met at a business conference hobson and lucas announced their engagement in january  and were married on june   at lucas skywalker ranch they have one daughter together everest hobson lucas who was born via surrogacy in august  hobson was photographed by annie leibovitz for the  pirelli calendar referencesedit  mellody hobson chair of the board of directors dreamworks animation website accessed   httpwwwchicagotribunecombusinessctmellodyhobsonchaireconomicclubbizstoryhtml  ariel investments llc ariel investments   httpwwwthehistorymakerscombiographybiographyaspbioindex  mellody hobson the worlds  most influential people time a