vestment and financial expertise to the board of directors ms hobsons experience as an onair cbs news contributor and analyst on finance and the economy provides insight into media and communications and public relations considerations ms hobson also brings to the board of directors valuable knowledge of corporate governance and similar issues from her service on other publicly traded companies boards of directors as well as her service on the securities and exchange commission sec investment advisory committee which advises the sec on matters of concern to investors in the securities markets in addition ms hobson has brand marketing experience through her service on the board of directors of the estee lauder companies and her past service on the dreamworks animation board prior to its acquisition by comcast corporation source starbucks corporation on    sign up for equilar atlas and view mellody l hobsons full profile by accessing equilar atlas you can view bios network salary and wealth events of industryleading executives like mellody l hobson more specifically youll be able to identify corporate executives in mellody l hobsons network and community follow changes in mellody l hobsons employment and moneyinmotion connect with mellody l hobson through your network of conections view full profile   search for over  executive profiles bio example mellody l hobson mellody l hobsons connections  sign up now to view mellody l hobsons  connections » j erik fyrwald board member lilly john w mccarter former board member ww grainger inc paul g allen former chairman charter communications inc sheryl k sandberg dir and chief operating officer facebook inc norman r bobins board member aar david a pace chief executive officer and director jamba inc frank ianna board member hrg group inc richard l keyser former chairman and ceo ww grainger inc howard d schultz executive chairman starbucks corporation charlene barshefsky board member american express popular profiles sign up now